text.tspan: *The average human takes 14 minutes to fall

flowRoot.flowPara: SLEEPO works by counting backwards in sleep cycles. Waking up in the middle of a sleep cycle leaves you feeling tired and groggy, but waking up in between cycles wakes you up feeling freshed and alert!
This tool will help you to sleep at the correct time.
If you know when you want to fall asleep, but not when you should wake up, choose this option.
If you know when you want to wake up, but not when you should sleep, choose this option.
